Custom cli for assimp (assimp ToolKit)

mkdir build
cd build
cmake .. -G"Unix Makefiles" -DASSIMP_DIR=path/to/assimp

Usage:
asstk [-o OUTFILE] [-f FORMAT] [-s SCALE] [-x] INFILE

-x: print exportable formats
-o: export model to. infers format from filename if possible, unless overridden by -f
-f: force export to specific format (number from -x listing)
-s: uniform scale model by a specific amount before exporting
